snippet.title: Lets Play: VIP (PS2) part 1.
snippet.description:
Hello peeps, and welcome to my new PS2 Lets Play: VIP Starring Pamela Anderson!

I don't even know what kind of game this is yet, fingers crossed it's an enjoyable one, but I highly doubt it lol! Ah well, sure there'll be plenty of risque photos and stuff to keep me entertained :D!

Thanks for watching and don't forget to rate, comment and subscribe!!!
